                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The graveknight unleashes a @Template[cone|distance:30] of energy. Creatures in the area take @Damage[21d6[mental]] with a @Check[will|dc:40|basic|options:area-effect] save.</p>\n<p>The graveknight can use this ability once every [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Devastating Blast]] rounds.</p>"
